Package com.heretere.hdl

Class DependencyEngine

java.lang.Object
com.heretere.hdl.DependencyEngine
public final class DependencyEngine
extends Object
A dependency engine is used as the starter point for adding dependencies to be downloaded and loaded at runtime.

    • createNew

      @Contract("_ -> new") @NotNull public static @NotNull DependencyEngine createNew​(@NotNull @NotNull Path basePath)
      Creates a new Dependency Engine with the specified base path. It includes all the default DependencyLoader's by default.

      For now that is just the maven dependency loader.

      Parameters:
      basePath - The base path for all dependencies to be downloaded.
      Returns:
      A new DependencyEngine.

    • addDependenciesFromClass

      @Contract("_ -> this") @NotNull public @NotNull DependencyEngine addDependenciesFromClass​(@NotNull @NotNull Class<?> clazz)
      Adds dependency annotations from a class to the currently loaded dependency loaders in this engine. These are not added retroactively, you need to add the dependency loaders first.
      Parameters:
      clazz - The class to load the annotations from.

      this
